504
00:24:41,780 --> 00:24:43,382
<i>Within a week, the shop had to close.</i>

505
00:24:43,382 --> 00:24:44,450
<i>The next episode...</i>

506
00:24:56,495 --> 00:24:59,965
Just bring it to me from
